  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    IDataFrame
    Common interface for dataframes in this project, most of the methods are implemented on table.Table.java.
    IDataFrameFactory
    Interface for dataframe factories (CSVFactory, JSONFactory, TXTFactory...)
